REFERENCE           OBJECTIVES
LANG_ENGLISH        "Objectives"
LANG_CZECH        "Cile"

REFERENCE           POWERDUEL_GAME_RULES_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Power Duel recreates epic lightsaber battles by pitting two opponents against a stronger opponent in a two-on-one match to the death.  All competitors start a round with full health, their sabers, and a blaster pistol (server option), but the lone opponent has an edge in health and Force ability.  Therefore, the teamed opponents must work together to defeat their stronger foe.  \n\nAny number of players can participate in Power Duel, but only three are in the arena at any given time.  Remaining players observe until a match is complete.  A match is completed when either side is eliminated.  The loser is put at the end of the observer queue, and the next person or persons in line are brought in to fight the winner.  If a member of the paired team is killed but the dual team wins, that player is still sent to the bottom of the list.  The surviving player or players are the only ones that stays in the game.  \n\nAll competitors are fully replenished with health and equipment.  The winner or winners continue to compete against new opponents, scoring points until he or she is eliminated or the match limit is reached.\n\nAs lone players get closer to the duel limit, they will start each match with lower health and power until they are equal to the players on the paired team.\n\nSCORING\n   Eliminating an enemy (dual team):  +1 point\n   Eliminating both enemies (lone team):  +1 point\n   Eliminating yourself (lone team):  +1 to your opponent\n\nThe player with the highest score at the end of the match wins."
LANG_CZECH        "Power Duel vytvari epicke bitvy se svetelnymi meci. Postavi dva protivniky proti jednomu silnejsimu v souboji dvou na jednoho na zivot a na smrt. Vsichni souperi zacinaji kolo\ns plnym zdravim, svymi meci a blastery (volitelna moznost serveru), ale osamoceny protivnik ma vyhodu ve vysi zdravi\na Sily. Proto musi tymovi protivnici spolupracovat, aby porazili sveho silnejsiho nepritele.\n\nPower Duelu se muze zucastnit libovolny pocet hracu, ale\nv jednom okamziku jsou v arene pouze tri. Zbyvajici hraci zapas pozoruji, dokud neskonci. Zapas konci, kdyz je eliminovana jedna ze stran. Ten kdo prohraje, skonci na konci rady pozorovatelu a do boje proti vitezi se zapoji nova osoba nebo osoby, ktere jsou na rade. Jestlize je zabit clen tymove dvojice, ale tento tym vyhraje, je hrac presto poslan na konec seznamu. Hrac nebo hraci, kteri preziji, jsou jedinymi, kteri zustanou ve hre.\n\nVsem souperum je zcela doplneno zdravi a vybaveni. Vitez nebo vitezove pokracuji v boji proti novym protivnikum\na ziskavaji body, dokud nejsou eliminovani nebo nevyprsi limit zapasu.\n\nJak se osameli hraci blizi ke konci zapasu, zacinaji kazdy dalsi zapas s nizsim zdravim a Silou, dokud nebudou vyrovnani\ns hraci v tymove dvojici.\n\nBODOVANI\n   Eliminace nepritele (tymova dvojice):  +1 bod\n   Eliminace obou nepratel (osamely hrac):  +1 bod\n   Vlastni eliminace (osamely hrac):  +1 bod nepriteli\n\nHrac s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vitezi."

REFERENCE           SIEGE_GAME_RULES_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Siege pits two teams against each other in a timed match in which one team is on offense and the other on defense.  Both teams have objectives, but the offensive team must complete their primary objectives to win.\n\nEach team is made up of a number of characters, each with their own specialty.  Every character can contribute with their own unique skill set.\n\nAn optional server rule allows for team switching.  With this option enabled, teams switch after the first match.  If the offensive team had won the first match, the new offensive team has a time limit equal to the time it took the first team to win.  If the offensive team completes all the objectives in the shorter time limit, they win the game.\n\nWIN CONDITIONS - OFFENSE\n  Complete all primary objectives before time runs out.\n\nWIN CONDITIONS - DEFENSE\n  Prevent offense from completing all primary objectives before time runs out.\n  Complete objectives which may prevent the offensive team from completing any of their primary objectives."
LANG_CZECH        "Siege postavi proti sobe dva tymy v casove omezenem zapase, ve kterem jeden tym utoci a druhy se brani. Oba tymy maji sve cile, ale utocici tym musi splnit sve primarni cile, aby vyhral.\n\nKazdy tym tvori nekolik postav, kazda se svoji vlastni specializaci.  Kazda postava muze prispet svoji vlastni unikatni sadou dovednosti.\n\nVolitelne pravidlo serveru umoznuje prepinani pozic tymu.\nS touto volbou zapnutou se tymy vymeni po prvnim zapase.  Jestlize utocici tym vyhral prvni zapas, ma novy utocici tym casovy limit rovnajici se tomu, jak dlouho trvalo prvnimu tymu vyhrat.  Jestlize utocici tym splni vsechny cile v kratsim casovem limitu, vyhrava hru.\n\nPODMINKY PRO VITEZSTVI - UTOCICI\n  Splnit vsechny primarni cile drive, nez vyprsi cas.\n\nPODMINKY PRO VITEZSTVI - BRANICI\n  Zabranit utocicim ve splneni vsech primarnich cilu drive, nez vyprsi cas.\n  Splnit cile, ktere mohou zabranit utocicimu tymu ve splneni jakehokoliv z jejich primarnich cilu."

REFERENCE           THE_GAME_OF_DUEL_IS_ALSO
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel pits two combatants in a small enclosed arena to battle with lightsabers.  Both competitors start a round with full health, their sabers, and a blaster pistol (server option), and must face off against one another. \n\nAny number of players can participate in Duel, but only two are in the arena at any given time.  Remaining players observe until a match is complete.  When one player is eliminated, the loser is put at the end of the observer queue, and the next person in line is brought in to fight the winner.  \n\nOnce again, both competitors are fully replenished with health.  The winner continues to compete against new opponents, scoring points until he or she is eliminated or the match limit is reached.\n\nSCORING\n   Eliminating an enemy:  +1 point\n   Eliminating yourself:     +1 to your opponent\n\nThe player with the highest score at the end of the match wins."
LANG_CZECH        "Duel postavi dva bojovniky do male uzavrene areny, kde bojuji se svetelnymi meci.  Oba souperi zacinaji kolo s plnym zdravim, svymi meci a blasterem (volitelna moznost serveru) a musi celit jeden druhemu.\n\nDuelu se muze zucastnit libovolny pocet hracu, ale v jednom okamziku jsou v arene pouze dva.  Zbyvajici hraci zapas pozoruji, dokud neskonci.  Kdyz je jeden z hracu eliminovan, skonci na konci rady pozorovatelu a do boje proti vitezi se zapoji nova osoba, ktera je na rade.  \n\nObema souperum je opet doplneno zdravi.  Vitez pokracuje\nv boji proti novym protivnikum a ziskava body, dokud neni eliminovan nebo nevyprsi limit zapasu.\n\nBODOVANI\n  Eliminace nepritele: +1 bod\n  Vlastni eliminace: +1 bod protivnikovi\n\nHrac s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vitezi."

REFERENCE           THIS_GAME_PITS_TWO_JEDI
LANG_ENGLISH        "Team Free For All pits two Jedi teams against each other in a battle for supremacy.  Each player scores points for eliminating opponents, but players on the same team can work together to eliminate tougher foes.  All players on a team combine their scores for a single team score.\n\nWeapons and equipment are acquired in the field unless otherwise specified on the server.  Some options include whether to allow Force powers or not and the maximum Force Level available.\n\nSCORING\n   Eliminating a member of the enemy team:  +1 point\n   Eliminating yourself or a team member:     -1 point\n\nThe team with the highest score at the end of the round wins the game. "
LANG_CZECH        "Team Free For All postavi proti sobe dva tymy Jediu v bitve\no nadvladu.  Kazdy hrac ziskava body za eliminaci protivniku, ale hraci ve stejnem tymu mohou spolupracovat pri eliminaci tuzsich nepratel.  Skore vsech hracu v tymu se scita do jednoho tymoveho skore.\n\nZbrane a vybaveni se ziskavaji v poli, neni-li serverem urceno jinak.  Mezi moznosti patri zda povolit Silu nebo ne\na maximalni dostupna uroven Sily.\n\nBODOVANI\n  Eliminace clena nepratelskeho tymu: +1 bod\n  Vlastni eliminace nebo eliminace clena sveho tymu: -1 bod\n\nTym s nejvyssim skore na konci kola vyhrava hru."

REFERENCE           IN_CAPTURE_THE_FLAG_CTF
LANG_ENGLISH        "In Capture The Flag (CTF), two teams compete to capture the flag of the opposing team and return it to their home base.  Any member of a team can pick up the opposing team's flag.  When the flag is taken, all players on the map are alerted to the event.  The flag carrier must then escape from the enemy's territory and return with the flag to their own base to score.  \n\nIf the flag carrier is eliminated, the flag is dropped at the point of elimination. If a member of the flag owner's team touches the flag, it is automatically returned to their base. If a member of the eliminated player's team picks it up, they can continue to try to return it to their home base.  The flag carrier's own flag must be 'home' at its base position for the carrier to score with the opposing team's flag.\n\nTEAM SCORING\n  Capturing the enemy's flag:  +1 point\n\nINDIVIDUAL SCORING\n  Picking up enemy's flag:  +10 points\n  Capturing the enemy's flag:  +100 points\n  Your team captures enemy's flag:  +25 points\n  Recovering your flag:  +10 points\n  - allowing immediate capture for team: +10 points\n  Eliminating enemy flag carrier:  +20 points\n  - allowing immediate capture for team: +10 points\n  Protecting your flag carrier:  +5 points\n  Protecting your flag base:  +10 points\n\nThe team with the highest score at the end of the match wins the game."
LANG_CZECH        "V Capture The Flag (CTF) se dva tymy snazi sebrat vlajku druheho tymu a donest ji do sve vlastni zakladny.  Vlajku nepratelskeho tymu muze sebrat jakykoliv clen tymu.  Kdyz je vlajka sebrana, jsou vsichni hraci na mape na tuto udalost upozorneni.  Nositel vlajky musi pote uniknout\nz nepratelskeho uzemi a vratit se s vlajkou do sve vlastni zakladny, aby skoroval.\n\nJe-li nositel vlajky eliminovan, je vlajka upustena na miste eliminace.  Jestlize se vlajky dotkne clen tymu, kteremu vlajka patri, je vlajka automaticky vracena do jeho zakladny.  Jestlize vlajku sebere clen tymu, jehoz hrac byl eliminovan, muze pokracovat v pokusu donest ji do sve vlastni zakladny.  Vlastni vlajka nositele musi byt 'doma' v zakladni pozici, aby mohl nositel skorovat s vlajkou nepratelskeho tymu.\n\nTYMOVE BODOVANI\n  Doneseni vlajky nepritele: +1 bod\n\nINDIVIDUALNI BODOVANI\n  Sebrani vlajky nepritele: +10 bodu\n Doneseni vlajky nepritele: +100 bodu\n  Vas tym donese vlajku nepritele: +25 bodu\n Ziskani zpet Vasi vlajky: +10 bodu\n - v pripade ze to umozni okamzite doneseni vlajky nepritele: +10 bodu\n  Eliminace nepratelskeho nositele vlajky: +20 bodu\n  - v pripade ze to umozni okamzite doneseni vlajky nepritele: +10 bodu\n  Ubraneni Vaseho nositele vlajky: +5 bodu\n  Ubraneni Vasi vlajky v zakladne: +10 bodu\n\nTym s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vyhrava hru."

REFERENCE           CAPTURE_THE_YSALIMIRI
LANG_ENGLISH        "Capture the Ysalamiri is similar to Capture The Flag, but the standard flag is replaced by a red or blue branch that carries a Ysalamiri, a lizard which dampens all Force capabilities when carried.  The carrier cannot use any Force powers (such as Force Jump or Speed) to hastily return the flag to their home base, but opponents cannot use their Force powers directly against that player either.\n\nTwo teams compete to capture each other's Ysalamiri branch and return it to their home base.  Any member of a team can enter enemy territory and pick up the Ysalamiri branch. When the branch is stolen, all players on the map are alerted to the event.  The carrier must then escape from the enemy's territory and return with the Ysalamiri branch to their own base to score.  If the carrier is eliminated, the Ysalamiri branch pops out and is left behind.  If a member of the owner's team touches the Ysalamiri branch, it is automatically returned to their base.  If a member of the Ysalamiri branch thief's team picks it up, they can continue to try to return it to their home base.  The carrier's own flag must be 'home' at its base position for the carrier to score with the opposing team's Ysalamiri branch.\n\nTEAM SCORING\n      Capturing the enemy's branch:  +1 point\n\nINDIVIDUAL SCORING\n      Picking up enemy's branch:  +10 points\n      Capturing the enemy's branch:  +100 points\n      Your team captures enemy's branch:  +25 points\n      Recovering your branch:  +10 points\n      - allowing immediate capture for team: +10 points\n      Eliminating enemy branch carrier:  +20 points\n      - allowing immediate capture for team: +10 points\n      Protecting your branch carrier:  +5 points\n      Protecting your branch base:  +10 points\n\nThe team with the highest score at the end of the match wins the game."
LANG_CZECH        "Typ Capture the Ysalamiri je podobny Capture The Flag, ale standardni vlajka je nahrazena cervenou nebo modrou vetvi, na ktere sedi Ysalamiri, jesterka, ktera kdyz je nesena, utlumuje veskerou Silu.  Nositel nemuze pouzivat zadnou Silu (jako je Skok nebo Rychlost), aby rychle donesl vetev do sve vlastni zakladny, ale ani protivnici nemohou pouzivat svoji Silu primo proti tomuto hraci.\n\nDva tymy se snazi sebrat vetev s Ysalamiri toho druheho a donest ji do sve vlastni zakladny.  Jakykoliv clen tymu muze vstoupit na nepratelske uzemi a sebrat vetev s Ysalamiri.  Kdyz je vetev s Ysalamiri ukradena, jsou vsichni hraci na mape na tuto udalost upozorneni.  Nositel musi pote uniknout z nepratelskeho uzemi a vratit se s vetvi s Ysalamiri do sve vlastni zakladny, aby skoroval.  Jestlize je nositel eliminovan, vetev s Ysalamiri vyskoci a zustane na miste.  Jestlize se vetve s Ysalamiri dotkne clen tymu, jemuz Ysalamiri patri, je vetev automaticky vracena do jeho zakladny.  Jestlize vetev s Ysalamiri sebere clen tymu, ktery vetev ukradl, muze pokracovat v pokusu donest ji do sve vlastni zakladny.  Vlastni vetev nositele musi byt 'doma' v zakladni pozici, aby mohl nositel skorovat s vetvi s Ysalamiri nepratelskeho tymu.\n\nTYMOVE BODOVANI\n  Doneseni vetve nepritele: +1 bod\n\nINDIVIDUALNI BODOVANI\n  Sebrani vetve nepritele: +10 bodu\n  Doneseni vetve nepritele: +100 bodu\n  Vas tym donese vetev nepritele: +25 bodu\n Ziskate zpet svoji vetev: +10 bodu\n - pokud to umozni okamzite doneseni vetve nepritele: +10 bodu\n  Eliminace nepratelskeho nositele vetve: +20 bodu\n - pokud to umozni okamzite doneseni vetve nepritele: + 10 bodu\n  Ubraneni Vaseho nositele vetve: +5 bodu\n  Ubraneni vetve ve Vasi zakladne: +10 bodu\n\nTym s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vyhrava hru."

REFERENCE           THIS_GAME_IS_BEST_SUMMED
LANG_ENGLISH        "Free For All is best summed up as every person for themselves.  Players score points by eliminating other players and no one can be considered an ally. \n\nWeapons and equipment are acquired in the field unless otherwise specified on the server.  Some options include whether to allow Force powers or not and the maximum Force Level available.\n\nSCORING\n   Eliminating an enemy:  +1 point\n   Eliminating yourself:     -1 point\n\nThe player with the highest score at the end of the match wins the game."
LANG_CZECH        "Free For All se necha nejlepe shrnout jako kazdy za sebe.  Hraci ziskavaji body eliminaci ostatnich hracu a nikoho nelze povazovat za spojence. \n\nZbrane a vybaveni se ziskavaji v poli, neni-li serverem urceno jinak.  Mezi moznosti patri zda povolit Silu nebo ne\na maximalni dostupna uroven Sily.\n\nBODOVANI\n  Eliminace nepritele: +1 bod\n  Vlastni eliminace: -1 bod\n\nHrac s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vyhrava hru."

REFERENCE           A_LIGHTSABER_IS_PLACED
LANG_ENGLISH        "A lightsaber is placed at a single point on the map.  All players start and respawn with standard default weapons (no lightsaber) and must obtain additional weaponry in the field.  While players may eliminate one another at any time, no player can score any points until one player picks up the lightsaber.  Once a player grabs the lightsaber, he/she becomes the 'Jedi Master' and is immediately imbued with rank 3 in every Force power and can only use the lightsaber for a weapon.   Any player the Jedi Master eliminates by any means scores a point.  If friendly fire is on, any player that any other player eliminates also gives the Jedi Master a point.  When the Jedi Master is eliminated, the lightsaber is thrown out a short distance from their body in the direction of the player who eliminated the Jedi Master.  The former Jedi Master is respawned as a normal non-Jedi, and whoever picks up the fallen lightsaber becomes the new 'Master.'\n\nSCORING\n   Eliminating an enemy while Jedi Master:  +1 point\n   Eliminating yourself while Jedi Master:  -1 point\n   Eliminating Jedi Master in play:  +1 point\n   Eliminating any non-Jedi while Jedi Master in play:  +1 point for Jedi Master\n   Eliminating any non-Jedi while no Jedi Master in play:  0 points\n\nThe player with the highest score at the end of the match wins."
LANG_CZECH        "Na jedno misto na mape je umisten svetelny mec. Vsichni hraci zacinaji a opetovne se objevuji se standardnimi zbranemi (bez svetelneho mece) a musi si ziskat dalsi zbrane v poli.  I kdyz hraci mohou kdykoliv eliminovat jeden druheho, nemuze zadny hrac ziskat body, dokud jeden z hracu nesebere svetelny mec.  Jakmile nejaky hrac svetelny mec sebere, stane se 'Mistrem Jedi' a okamzite ziska treti stupen u kazdeho druhu Sily a jako zbran muze pouzivat pouze svetelny mec.  Za kazdeho hrace, ktereho Mistr Jedi eliminuje, dostava bod.  Je-li zapnuta palba na spojence, tak kazdy eliminovany hrac od jineho hrace take prida bod Mistru Jedi. Kdyz je Mistr Jedi eliminovan, je svetelny mec odhozen na kratkou vzdalenost od jeho tela ve smeru hrace, ktery Mistra Jedi eliminoval.  Byvali Mistr Jedi se objevi znovu jako normalni hrac a kdokoliv, kdo sebere spadly svetelny mec, se stava novym 'Mistrem'.\n\nBODOVANI\n  Eliminace nepritele, kdyz jste Mistr Jedi: +1 bod\n  Vlastni eliminace, kdyz jste Mistr jedi: -1 bod\n  Eliminace Mistra Jedi: +1 bod\n  Eliminace jakehokoliv normalniho hrace, existuje-li Mistr Jedi: +1 bod pro Mistra Jedi\n  Eliminace jakehokoliv normalniho hrace, neexistuje-li Mistr Jedi: 0 bodu\n\nHrac s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vitezi."

REFERENCE           THIS_GAME_IS_SIMILAR
LANG_ENGLISH        "This game is similar to Free For All with one exception: players start with no Force powers whatsoever.  Scattered throughout the map are a number of ancient Holocrons (Force cubes), which represent the various Force abilities. Any player can pick up the Holocrons and each one provides the full three ranks of its represented Force power. If a player is eliminated, his Holocrons pop out from where his body fell and become available for other players to grab.  If a dropped Holocron is not grabbed within 30 seconds, it disappears and respawns in its standard starting location.  A single player cannot collect more than three of the Holocrons simultaneously (unless otherwise specified on the server).  When a player picks up a fourth, the Holocron they've possessed the longest pops out for someone else to grab.\n\nSCORING\n   Eliminating an enemy:  +1 point\n   Eliminating yourself:  -1 point\n\nThe player with the highest score at the end of the match wins."
LANG_CZECH        "Tato hra je podobna Free For All s jedinou vyjimkou: hraci zacinaji bez jakekoliv Sily.  Po mape je roztrouseno mnozstvi starovekych holocronu (krychli Sily), ktere predstavuji ruzne druhy Sily.  Jakykoliv hrac muze holocrony sebrat a kazdy z nich nabizi vsechny tri stupne jim predstavovane Sily.  Jestlize je hrac eliminovan, jeho holocrony vyskoci z mista, kde padlo jeho telo a zpristupni se k sebrani ostatnim hracum.  Jestlize neni upusteny holocron sebran do triceti vterin, zmizi a objevi se znovu na sve puvodni startovni pozici.  Jeden hrac nemuze naraz sebrat vice nez tri holocrony (pokud neni serverem urceno jinak).  Kdyz hrac sebere ctvrty holocron, tak ten jenz mel u sebe nejdele, vyskoci a muze ho sebrat nekdo jiny.\n\nBODOVANI\n  Eliminace nepritele: +1 bod\n  Vlastni eliminace: -1 bod\n\nHrac s nejvyssim skore na konci zapasu vitezi."

REFERENCE           DURATION_IMMEDIATE_NAREA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Jump\nDuration: Immediate\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only \nEffect: Allows Jedi to make a tremendous vertical leap.\n\n  Rank 1 - Jedi can leap up to twice their normal jump height.\n  Rank 2 - Jedi can leap up to four times their normal jump height.\n  Rank 3 - Jedi can leap up to eight times their normal jump height."
LANG_CZECH        "Skok\nTrvani: Bezprostredni\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi \nUcinek: Umozni Jedimu provest obrovsky skok do vysky.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Jedi muze vyskocit az do dvojnasobku vysky sveho normalniho skoku.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi muze vyskocit az do ctyrnasobku vysky sveho normalniho skoku.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi muze vyskocit az do osminasobku vysky sveho normalniho skoku."

REFERENCE           DURATION_5_SECONDS_NAREA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Speed\nDuration: Variable (10 - 20 seconds)\nArea Of Effect: Jedi\nEffect: Jedi speeds up.\n\n  Rank 1 - The Jedi moves 25% faster than normal for 10 seconds\n  Rank 2 - The Jedi moves 50% faster than normal for 15 seconds\n  Rank 3 - The Jedi moves 75% faster than normal for 20 seconds"
LANG_CZECH        "Rychlost\nTrvani: Ruzne (10 - 20 sekund)\nOblast ucinku: Jedi\nUcinek: Jedi zrychli.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Jedi se pohybuje o 25% rychleji nez normalne po 10 sekund.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi se pohybuje o 50% rychleji nez normalne po 15 sekund.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi se pohybuje o 75% rychleji nez normalne po 20 sekund."

REFERENCE           DURATION_INSTANTANEOUS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Push\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Objects or Persons\nEffect: Allows Jedi to push objects away from themselves, deflect missiles, and defend against Force Grip and Force Push attacks.\n\n  Rank 1 - Jedi uses the Force to push a specific enemy or object focused on.\n  Rank 2 - Jedi uses the Force to push back multiple enemies or objects in a limited arc.\n  Rank 3 - Jedi can push back multiple enemies with enough force to do damage by pushing the enemies into solid surfaces or off ledges."
LANG_CZECH        "Odstrceni\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Predmety nebo osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu odsouvat od sebe predmety, odrazet strely a branit se proti Sevreni a Odstrceni.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Jedi pouziva Silu k odstrceni specifickeho nepritele nebo predmetu, na ktery se zameruje.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi pouziva Silu k odstrceni nekolika nepratel nebo predmetu v omezene vyseci.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi muze odstrcit nekolik nepratel s dostatecnou silou, aby je zranil tim, ze je odstrci na prekazky nebo dolu\nz okraju."

REFERENCE           INSTANTANEOUS_EFFECT_NAREA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Pull\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Objects or Persons\nEffect: Allows Jedi to pull enemies towards themselves with a chance of disarming the opponent.  It also defends against Force Pull attacks.\n\n  Rank 1 - Jedi uses the Force to pull a specific enemy focused on.\n  Rank 2 - Jedi uses the Force to pull multiple enemies in a limited arc.\n  Rank 3 - Jedi can pull multiple enemies with enough force to knock targets down at close range. "
LANG_CZECH        "Pritahnuti\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Predmety nebo osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu pritahnout k sobe nepritele\ns moznosti, ze protivnika odzbroji.  Take brani pred Pritahnutim.\n\n Stupen 1 - Jedi pouziva Silu k pritahnuti specifickeho nepritele, na ktereho se zameruje.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi pouziva Silu k pritahnuti nekolika nepratel\nv omezene vyseci.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi muze pritahnout nekolik nepratel\ns dostatecnou silou na to, aby je na kratkou vzdalenost srazil k zemi."

REFERENCE           EFFECT_NAREA_OF_EFFECT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Sense\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Jedi field of view\nEffect: Allows Jedi great and wide vision.\n\nForce seeing allows the Jedi to see all enemies clearly, regardless of lighting conditions, by surrounding them with an easy-to-see glowing aura. Force seeing also allows Jedi to counteract the Jedi Mind Trick Force power. At the highest level of Force Seeing the Jedi develops a sixth sense that allows him to dodge sniper fire. \n\n  Rank 1 - See players' auras highlighted in view with normal time duration.\n  Rank 2 - See players' auras in view and through walls with double time duration.\n  Rank 3 - See players' auras in view and through walls at any range with triple time duration. Players can automatically dodge sniper shots at this level."
LANG_CZECH        "Intuice\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Kam Jedi dohledne\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu silny a daleky zrak\n\nIntuice umoznuje Jedimu videt jasne vsechny nepratele bez ohledu na svetelne podminky tim, ze je obklopi snadno viditelnou zarici aurou.  Intuice take umoznuje Jedimu rusit Oklamani smyslu. Na nejvyssim stupni Intuice si Jedi vyvine sesty smysl, ktery mu umoznuje uskocit pred strelou\nz odstrelovacky. \n\n  Stupen 1 - Vidi vysvicene aury hracu v dohledu po normalni dobu.\n  Stupen 2 - Vidi aury hracu v dohledu a skrz zdi po dvojnasobnou dobu.\n  Stupen 3 - Vidi aury hracu v dohledu a skrz zdi na jakoukoliv vzdalenost po trojnasobnou dobu.  Na tomto stupni mohou hraci automaticky uskocit pred strelou z odstrelovacky."

REFERENCE           DURATION_VARIABLE_NAREA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Protection\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Jedi Only\nEffect: Protects from physical attack.\n\nDamage to Jedi from Physical attacks is taken from Force Power pool rather than from health score.\n\n  Rank 1 - 50% Damage blocked, 100% removed from Force pool, max 100 Damage\n  Rank 2 - 75% Damage blocked, 50% removed from Force pool, max 200 Damage\n  Rank 3 - 87.5% Damage blocked, 25% removed from Force pool, max 400 Damage"
LANG_CZECH        "Ochrana\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Chrani pred fyzickym utokem.\n\nPoraneni Jediho fyzickym utokem odebira Silu misto zdravi.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Blokuje 50% poraneni, 100% ze zbytku vzato ze Sily, maximalni poraneni 100.\n  Stupen 2 - Blokuje 75% poraneni, 50% ze zbytku vzato ze Sily, maximalni poraneni 200.\n  Stupen 3 - Blokuje 87.5% poraneni, 25% ze zbytku vzato ze Sily, maximalni poraneni 400."

REFERENCE           DURATION_CONTINUOUS_NAREA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Absorption\nDuration: Continuous\nArea Of Effect: Jedi Only\nEffect: Protects from any direct Force Powers.\n\nAbsorbs damage from Force abilities directed at the wielder and turns that energy into usable Force Power.\n\n  Rank 1 - Nullifies rank 1 Force attacks, reduces the effect of higher rank Force attacks.  Returns some Force Power.\nRank 2 - Nullifies rank 2 Force attacks, greatly reduces the effect of higher rank Force attacks.  Returns greater Force Power.\nRank 3 - Nullifies all Force attacks.  Returns even greater Force Power. "
LANG_CZECH        "Pohlceni\nTrvani: Nepretrzite\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Chrani pred vsemi primymi Silami.\n\nPohlcuje poraneni ze Sily namirene na Jediho a premenuje tuto energii na vyuzitelnou Silu.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Rusi utoky Silou prvniho stupne, snizuje ucinek utoku Silou vyssiho stupne.  Vraci cast Sily.\nStupen 2 - Rusi utoky Silou druheho stupne, znacne snizuje ucinek utoku Silou vyssiho stupne.  Vraci vice Sily.\nStupen 3 - Rusi vsechny utoky Silou.  Vraci jeste vice Sily."

REFERENCE           OF_EFFECT_JEDI_ONLY_NEFFECT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Heal\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: The Jedi heals after injury.\n\n  Rank 1 - Jedi regains up to 5 health instantly.\n  Rank 2 - Jedi regains up to 10 health instantly.\n  Rank 3 - Jedi regains up to 25 health instantly."
LANG_CZECH        "Leceni\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Jedi se vyleci po zraneni.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Jedi ziska okamzite az 5 bodu zdravi.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi ziska okamzite az 10 bodu zdravi.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi ziska okamzite az 25 bodu zdravi."

REFERENCE           DURATION_VARIABLE_20
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mind Trick\nDuration: Variable (5 - 15 seconds)\nArea Of Effect: Other Players\nEffect: Allows Jedi to make themselves invisible to other players.\n\n  Rank 1 - A Jedi is invisible to a single targeted enemy for 5 seconds.\n  Rank 2 - A Jedi is invisible to enemies in a forward arc of moderate distance for 10 seconds.\n  Rank 3 - A Jedi is invisible to all enemies in a moderate distance for 15 seconds."
LANG_CZECH        "Oklamani smyslu\nTrvani: Ruzne (5 - 15 sekund)\nOblast ucinku: Ostatni hraci\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu zneviditelnit se ostatnim hracum.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Jedi je neviditelny jednomu zamerenemu nepriteli po 5 sekund.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi je neviditelny nepratelum pred sebou\nv prumerne vzdalenosti po 10 sekund.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi je neviditelny vsem nepratelum v prumerne vzdalenosti po 15 sekund."

REFERENCE           OF_EFFECT_JEDI_ALLIES_NEFFECT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Heal Other\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Jedi allies\nEffect: The Jedi has the ability to heal allies after injury. \n\nForce Heal Other allows Jedi to restore a certain amount of health to their allies within a certain radius of their body.  Jedi can restore 50 health to one ally,\n33 health to two allies or 25 health to 3 or more allies.\n\n  Rank 1 - Normal range\n  Rank 2 - One and a half times normal range\n  Rank 3 - Double normal range"
LANG_CZECH        "Leceni druhych\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Jediho spojenci\nUcinek: Jedi ma schopnost lecit spojence pote, co byli zraneni.\n\nLeceni druhych umoznuje Jedimu obnovit urcite mnozstvi zdravi svym spojencum v urcitem okruhu kolem sveho tela.  Jedi muze obnovit 50 bodu zdravi jednomu spojenci,\n33 bodu zdravi dvema spojencum nebo 25 bodu zdravi trem nebo vice spojencum\n\n  Stupen 1 - Normalni dosah.\n  Stupen 2 - Jeden a pulkrat vetsi dosah.\n  Stupen 3 - Dvojnasobny dosah."

REFERENCE           DURATION_INSTANTANEOUS_NAREA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Grip\nDuration: Instantaneous\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to choke or constrict the organs of a living being.\n\n  Rank 1 - Affected enemy is gripped and held undamaged, but immobile for 5 seconds.  Jedi must remain stationary.\n  Rank 2 - Enemy is affected similarly to  rank 1, but the grip can damage and lift enemies with prolonged focus of the grip.  Jedi must remain stationary.\n  Rank 3 - Enemy is affected similarly to rank 2, but the Jedi can move freely and smash the enemy into walls and other obstacles or use the enemy as a shield while still doing choke damage."
LANG_CZECH        "Sevreni\nTrvani: Okamzite\nOblast ucinku: Pouze zive osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu skrtit nebo stisknout organy zivych bytosti.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Zasazeny nepritel je drzen a nezranen, ale je nepohyblivy po 5 sekund.  Jedi se nesmi hybat.\n  Stupen 2 - Nepritel je zasazen podobne jako pri prvnim stupni, ale sevreni ho muze poranit a vyzdvihnout s prodlouzenym ucinkem stisku.  Jedi se nesmi hybat.\n  Stupen 3 - Nepritel je zasazen podobne jako pri druhem stupni, ale Jedi se muze volne pohybovat a prastit s nepritelem o zed a ostatni prekazky nebo pouzit nepritele jako stit a pritom ho stale zranovat skrcenim."

REFERENCE           VARIABLE_NAREA_OF_EFFECT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Drain\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Drains Force Power and uses it to replenish life.\n\n  Rank 1 - Launches a single bolt that fires forward, draining 10 Force points per second and healing that amount.\n  Rank 2 - An un-aimed, continuous attack, draining 15 Force points per second.\n  Rank 3 - Emanates a sustained fan in a large forward arc, draining any target in front of him of 20 Force points per second."
LANG_CZECH        "Odcerpani\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze zive osoby\nUcinek: Odcerpava Silu a pouziva ji k doplneni zdravi.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Vypusti jeden blesk, ktery vystreli kupredu a cerpa 10 bodu Sily za sekundu a stejne mnozstvi prida ke zdravi.\n  Stupen 2 - Nemireny trvaly utok, ktery cerpa 15 bodu Sily za sekundu.\n  Stupen 3 - Vyzaruje pred sebe nepretrzity kuzel ve velke vyseci a cerpa z jakehokoliv cile pred sebou 20 bodu Sily za sekundu."

REFERENCE           OF_EFFECT_LIVING_PERSONS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Lightning\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to hurl a devastating electrical attack against enemies.\n\n  Rank 1 - Jedi launches a single bolt that fires forward, doing instant damage.\n  Rank 2 - Jedi can maintain the Force Lightning for a sustained forward attack.\n  Rank 3 - Jedi emanate a sustained fan of electricity in a large forward arc, damaging anything in front of them.  "
LANG_CZECH        "Blesk\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze zive bytosti\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu vyslat devastujici elektricky vyboj proti nepratelum.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Jedi vypusti jeden blesk, ktery vystreli kupredu\na zpusobi okamzite poraneni.\n  Stupen 2 - Jedi muze udrzet Blesk pro trvaly utok smerem kupredu.\n  Stupen 3 - Jedi vyzaruje pred sebe nepretrzity kuzel elektriny ve velke vyseci a zranuje vsechno pred sebou."

REFERENCE           DURATION_VARIABLE_10
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Rage\nDuration: Variable (10 - 30 seconds)\nArea Of Effect: Dark Jedi Only\nEffect: Jedi goes into a frenzy of speed for a given duration, but must recover afterwards. Drains health while active, and expires after the duration or when health hits 1.\n\nDark Rage:  Fire 33% faster, Move 100% faster, decrease damage taken by 50%, wielder cannot die (health stays at 1).\nDark Rage Recovery:  Fire 50% slower, move at 75% speed\n\n  Rank 1 - Rage for 10 seconds, 10 second recovery\n  Rank 2 - Rage for 20 seconds, 10 second recovery\n  Rank 3 - Rage for 30 seconds, 10 second recovery"
LANG_CZECH        "Temna zurivost\nTrvani: Ruzne (10 - 30 sekund)\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Temny Jedi\nUcinek: Jedi se dostane do zurive extaze na urcitou dobu, ale pote se musi regenerovat.  Je-li aktivni, cerpa zdravi a konci uplynutim doby, nebo kdyz zdravi dosahne jednoho bodu.\n\nTemna zurivost:  Strili o 33% rychleji, pohybuje se o 100% rychleji, snizuje utrzene poraneni o 50%, Jedi nemuze zemrit (zdravi zustava na 1).\nZotaveni po Temne zurivosti: Strili o 50% pomaleji, pohybuje se 75%ni rychlosti.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Zurivost po 10 sekund, zotaveni trva 10 sekund.\n  Stupen 2 - Zurivost po 20 sekund, zotaveni trva 10 sekund.\n  Stupen 3 - Zurivost po 30 sekund, zotaveni trva 10 sekund."

REFERENCE           EFFECT_JEDI_ALLIES_NEFFECT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Team Energize\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Jedi Allies\nEffect: The Jedi has the ability to imbue allies with Force energy.\n\nForce Team Energize allows the Jedi to restore a certain amount of Force energy to his allies within a certain radius of his body. Jedi can restore 50 Force points to one ally, 33 Force points to two allies or 25 Force points to 3 or more allies.\n\n  Rank 1 - Normal range\n  Rank 2 - One and a half times normal range\n  Rank 3 - Double normal range"
LANG_CZECH        "Posileni tymu\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Jediho spojenci\nUcinek: Jedi ma schopnost nabit spojence Silou.\n\nPosileni tymu umoznuje Jedimu obnovit urcite mnozstvi Sily svym spojencum v urcitem okruhu kolem sveho tela.  Jedi muze obnovit 50 bodu Sily jednomu spojenci, 33 bodu Sily dvema spojencum nebo 25 bodu Sily trem nebo vice spojencum.\n\n  Stupen 1 - Normalni dosah.\n  Stupen 2 - Jeden a pulkrat vetsi dosah.\n  Stupen 3 - Dvojnasobny dosah."

REFERENCE           STUN_BATON
LANG_ENGLISH        "STUN BATON"
LANG_CZECH        "OBUSEK NA OMRACENI"

REFERENCE           COMMONLY_USED_TO_SUBDUE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Commonly used to subdue unruly prisoners, the stun baton was designed for use in melee combat where killing your opponent is not necessarily the desired outcome.\n\nPrimary Fire - Short range jabbing electrical stun attack\nSecondary Fire - None"
LANG_CZECH        "Obusek na omraceni se bezne pouziva k podrobeni vzpurnych veznu a byl navrzen pro pouziti v pranicich, kde zabiti Vaseho protivnika nutne neni pozadovanym vysledkem.\n\nPrimarni utok - Omracujici bodavy elektricky vyboj na kratkou vzdalenost\nSekundarni utok - Nic"

REFERENCE           LIGHTSABER
NOTES               "Used in weapon binding."
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lightsaber:"
LANG_CZECH        "Svetelny mec:"

REFERENCE           AN_ELEGANT_WEAPON_FOR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lightsaber\nAn elegant weapon for a more civilized age, the lightsaber is the preferred weapon of the Jedi Knight.  The lightsaber is an energy blade of great power that can be used by the wielder for both attack and defense.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Slashing and swinging attacks\nSecondary Fire -  Force powered saber throw\nDefensive Ability -  Deflects blaster and energy weapon fire, parries enemy lightsaber attacks\nAmmo Type -  N/A"
LANG_CZECH        "Svetelny mec\nSvetelny mec je elegantni zbrani pro civilizovanejsi vek a je uprednostnovan rytiri Jedi.  Svetelny mec je energetickou cepeli velke sily, ktera muze byt pouzita svym drzitelem jak\nk utoku tak k obrane.\n\nPrimarni utok - Sekani a svihani\nSekundarni utok - Hod mecem za pomoci Sily\nObranna schopnost - Odrazi strelbu z blasteru a dalsich energetickych zbrani, odvraci utoky nepratelskeho svetelneho mece\nDruh naboju - Zadne"

REFERENCE           BLASTER_PISTOL
LANG_ENGLISH        "BLASTER PISTOL"
LANG_CZECH        "BLASTEROVA PISTOLE"

REFERENCE           BLASTER_PISTOL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DL-44 Heavy Blaster Pistol\nOne of the most common weapons in the galaxy, the DL-44 Heavy Blaster pistol has a slow rate of fire, but is highly accurate.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire -  Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast\nAmmo Type -  Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Tezka blasterova pistole DL-44\nTezka blasterova pistole DL-44 je jednou z nejbeznejsich zbrani v galaxii. Ma nizkou kadenci, ale je vysoce presna.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundarni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           KYLE_KATARN_S_WEAPON
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kyle Katarn's weapon of choice, the Bryar Blaster Pistol is a common hand-held energy weapon with a slow rate of fire and incredible accuracy.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire -  Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast\nAmmo Type -  Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Blasterova pistole Bryar je oblibenou zbrani Kyle Katarna a beznou rucni energetickou zbrani s nizkou kadenci a neuveritelnou presnosti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundardni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\Druh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           BLASTER_RIFLE
LANG_ENGLISH        "BLASTER RIFLE"
LANG_CZECH        "BLASTEROVA PUSKA"

REFERENCE           THE_PRIMARY_WEAPON_OF
LANG_ENGLISH        "E-11 Blaster Rifle\nThe primary weapon of the Imperial forces, the E-11 is a sturdy and deadly blaster rifle capable of inflicting great damage despite its small size. The E-11's compact design makes it easy to carry and conceal.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Slow, single shot with moderate accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire -  Rapid, burst fire with low accuracy and expanded firing area\nAmmo Type -  Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Blasterova puska E-11\nE-11 je zakladni zbrani vojaku Imperia. Je to stabilni a smrtici blasterova puska schopna zpusobit velke skody navzdory sve male velikosti.  Kompaktni design E-11 umoznuje jeji snadne noseni a ukryti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se stredni presnosti\na velkou silou\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           THIS_NEFARIOUS_WEAPON
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tenloss DXR-6 Disruptor rifle\nThis nefarious weapon affects matter at the molecular level, ripping apart living material with ease.  Because of the weapon's inhumane nature, the DXR-6 is outlawed throughout the galaxy and is generally only used by scattered droid and Remnant forces. \n\nPrimary Fire -  Single shot with slow fire rate, and instant attack\nSecondary Fire -  Scoped mode: Single shot that must be first charged up, causes increased damage and has a high energy consumption\nAmmo Type -  Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Tenlosska disruptorova puska DXR-6\nTato ohavna zbran ovlivnuje hmotu na molekularni urovni\na snadno trha na kusy zivy material.  Vzhledem k nelidske povaze zbrane je DXR-6 zakazana v cele galaxii a obecne ji pouzivaji pouze roztrousene jednotky droidu a zbylych vojaku Imperia. \n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden vystrel s nizkou kadenci a okamzitym ucinkem\nSekundarni utok - Odstrelovaci mod: Jeden vystrel, ktery se musi nejprve nabit, zpusobuje vetsi poraneni a ma vysokou energetickou spotrebu\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           BOWCASTER
NOTES               "Used in weapon binding."
LANG_ENGLISH        "Bowcaster:"
LANG_CZECH        "Kuse:"

REFERENCE           THIS_ARCHAIC_LOOKING
LANG_ENGLISH        "Wookiee Bowcaster\nThis archaic-looking weapon fires powerful bolts of metal enveloped in pockets of energy.  Capable of inflicting incredible damage, the bowcaster requires tremendous physical strength to fire. Most bowcasters sold outside the Wookiee homeworld come equipped with self-cocking actions that allow physically weaker creatures to fire them.\n\nPrimary Fire - Charged energy buildup for multiple shots\nSecondary Fire - Extremely accurate, ricochet-capable single shot\nAmmo Type -  Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Wookijska kuse\nTato zastarale vyhlizejici zbran pali silne kovove strely zabalene do energetickych obalu.  Kuse je schopna zpusobit neuveritelne skody a ke strelbe z ni se vyzaduje ohromna fyzicka sila.  Vetsina kusi prodanych mimo wookijskou domovinu je vybavena samonatahovacim mechanismem, diky kteremu z nich mohou strilet i fyzicky slabsi bytosti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Vytrysk nabite energie rozdeleny do nekolika strel\nSekundardni utok - Jeden extremne presny vystrel, ktery se muze odrazet\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           THIS_DESTRUCTIVE_PROJECTILE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Imperial Heavy Repeater with Concussion Launcher\nThis destructive projectile weapon is extremely deadly, firing rapid streams of metal bullets. Imperial  forces use the Heavy Repeater's deadly suppressive fire and concussion launcher for crowd control and to spread heavy fire over\nlarge areas.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Fully automatic projectile fire\nSecondary Fire -  Single shot, concussion explosive round\nAmmo type -  Metallic bolts"
LANG_CZECH        "Tezky imperialni opakovac s odpalovacem narazovych granatu\nTato niciva strelna zbran je vysoce smrtici a pali rychle davky kovovych kulek.  Vojaci Imperia pouzivaji smrtici strelbu tezkeho opakovace a jeho odpalovac narazovych granatu\nk ovladnuti davu a k rozptyleni tezke palby po\nvelkych oblastech.\n\nPrimarni utok - Plne automaticka projektilova palba\nSekundarni utok - Jedna explozivni strela s narazovym granatem\nDruh naboju - Kovove kulky"

REFERENCE           COMMONLY_REFERRED_TO
LANG_ENGLISH        "Destructive Electro-Magnetic Pulse 2 Gun\nCommonly referred to as the DEMP 2, this pulse rifle is primarily used against droids and electrical devices.  The DEMP 2 fires high-powered ion bursts that disrupt electrical systems, and are most effective against personal shields.  Unlike previous incarnations of the weapon, the DEMP 2's ion charges are capable of damaging living material.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Single shot, does some damage to humans, extra damage to shields\nSecondary Fire - A charged shot that unleashes a nearly instantaneous shockwave that can knock enemies back\nAmmo Type -  Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Niciva elektromagneticka pulsni puska typu 2\nTato puska se bezne nazyva DEMP 2 a pouziva se predevsim proti droidum a elektrickym zarizenim.  DEMP 2 strili vysokoenergeticke iontove paprsky, ktere narusuji elektricke systemy a jsou prevelice ucinne proti osobnim stitum.  Oproti predchozim verzim teto zbrane jsou iontove naboje DEMP2 schopne poranit zivy material.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden vystrel, ktery trochu porani lidi a velmi poskodi stity\nSekundarni utok - Nabita strela, ktera temer okamzite vytvori sokovou vlnu, ktera muze srazit nepratele k zemi\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           WIDELY_USED_BY_THE_CORPORATE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Golan Arms FC1 Flechette Weapon\nWidely used by the Corporate Sector Authority's police squads, the FC1 fires shards of metal in a widespread pattern. The weapon is designed to hit multiple targets in close proximity, but great care must be taken to avoid ricochet damage.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Single shot, spread fire\nSecondary Fire -  Dual explosive shrapnel charges\nAmmo Type -  Metallic Bolts"
LANG_CZECH        "Golanska rucni flechettova zbran FC1\nFC1 je siroce pouzivana policejnimi jednotkami uradu firemniho sektoru a strili kovove strepiny v rozprostrenem vzorci.  Zbran je navrzena tak, aby zasahla nekolik cilu na malou vzdalenost, ale drzitel si musi davat pozor, aby se vyhnul nebezpeci odrazenych strel.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden rozprostreny vystrel\nSekundardni utok - Dvojite explozivni delove strely\nDruh naboju - Kovove kulky"

REFERENCE           THE_PLX_2M_IS_AN_EXTREMELY
LANG_ENGLISH        "Merr-Sonn PLX-2M Portable Missile System\nThe PLX-2M is an extremely powerful weapon that fires Arakyd 3T3 missiles.  The sheer explosive power of the PLX-2M makes it dangerous to fire blindly in close quarters, but is extremely effective when used as a 'smart' tracking weapon.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Fires a single, forward-firing explosive missile \nSecondary Fire -  Fires a single 'smart' missile that tracks acquired and locked targets\nAmmo Type -  Rockets"
LANG_CZECH        "Prenosny raketovy system Merr-Sonn PLX-2M\nPLX-2M je extremne silnou zbrani, ktera strili rakety Arakyd 3T3.  Pouha explozivni sila PLX-2M cini tuto zbran nebezpecnou pro strelbu naslepo v tesnych prostorach, ale je velice ucinna, pouzije-li se jako 'chytra' navadeci zbran.\n\nPrimarni utok - Strili jednu explozivni raketu letici rovne kupredu \nSekundarni utok - Strili jednu 'chytrou' raketu, ktera sleduje zamerene cile\nDruh naboju - Rakety"

REFERENCE           THE_THERMAL_DETONATOR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Thermal Detonator\nThe thermal detonator is a radius-damage grenade that releases a barrage of thermal energy capable of disintegrating all matter around it.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Grenade explodes after short duration\nSecondary Fire -  Grenade explodes on contact"
LANG_CZECH        "Termalni detonator\nTermalni detonator je granatem, ktery v urcitem okruhu kolem sebe uvolni vlnu termalni energie, ktera je schopna rozlozit veskerou hmotu.\n\nPrimarni utok - Granat exploduje po kratkem case\nSekundarni utok - Granat exploduje pri kontaktu"

REFERENCE           TRIP_MINES_CONSIST_OF
LANG_ENGLISH        "Trip Mines\nTrip mines consist of a beam projector affixed to a shaped explosive casing.  The laser activates when the mine is placed and extends a beam from the charge to the nearest surface that intersects its path.  If the beam is broken or the charge is fired upon, the mine detonates and causes radius damage to anything in range.\n\nPrimary Fire  -  Once placed, it detonates if the beam is broken or the mine is destroyed\nSecondary Fire - Once placed, it detonates if someone is in its proximity or the mine is destroyed.  There is no beam and it will not detonate for the user"
LANG_CZECH        "Nastrazne miny\nNastrazne miny se skladaji z projektoru paprsku pripevneneho\nk vytvarovanemu vybusnemu obalu.  Laser se aktivuje pri polozeni miny a paprsek saha od naloze k nejblizsi prekazce, ktera krizuje jeho cestu. Je-li paprsek prerusen nebo nekdo na minu vystreli, mina detonuje a zpusobi skody na vsem\nv urcitem okruhu kolem sebe.\n\nPrimarni utok - Po polozeni vybuchne, je-li paprsek prerusen nebo je mina znicena\nSekundarni utok - Po polozeni vybuchne, je-li nekdo v jeji blizkosti nebo je mina znicena.  Neexistuje zadny paprsek\na mina nevybuchne, kdyz se priblizi ten, kdo ji polozil"

REFERENCE           A_DETONATION_PACK_IS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Detonation Packs\nA detonation pack is essentially a small explosive device with a remote detonation trigger.  The pack is placed or thrown and can be detonated at will by the user.  Detonation packs are commonly used to ambush enemies or open sealed doors.\n\nPrimary Fire -  Throws charge at the user's feet\nSecondary Fire - Explodes all set charges"
LANG_CZECH        "Vybusne naloze\nVybusna naloz je v podstate male explozivni zarizeni\ns dalkovym ovladanim.  Majitel naloze ji muze polozit nebo hodit a pote ji odpalit podle vlastniho uvazeni.  Vybusne naloze se bezne pouzivaji k vytvareni lecky na nepratele nebo k otevreni zamcenych dveri.\n\nPrimarni utok - Hodi naloz k noham majitele\nSekundarni utok - Vyhodi do vzduchu vsechny polozene naloze"

REFERENCE           CONC_RIFLE
LANG_ENGLISH        "CONCUSSION RIFLE"
LANG_CZECH        "NARAZOVA PUSKA"

REFERENCE           CONC_RIFLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Stouker Concussion Rifle\nThe Stouker fires a concussive blast creating an explosion that spreads about 4 meters in diameter.\n\nPrimary Fire - Single shot, large explosive effect that damages everything, slow firing rate\nSecondary Fire - Fires a smaller projectile shot that has a smaller explosive radius but does much more damage in that radius and has a more severe recoil\nAmmo Type -  Metallic Bolts"
LANG_CZECH        "Narazova puska Stouker\nStouker strili narazovy vyboj, ktery vytvori explozi, ktera se rozsiri priblizne do ctyr metru v prumeru.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jedna rana, velky vybusny ucinek, ktery poskodi vsechno, nizka kadence\nSekundarni utok - Strili mensi projektil, ktery ma mensi polomer vybuchu, ale v tomto okruhu nadela vice skod a ma silnejsi zpetny raz\nDruh naboju - Kovove kulky"

